java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class PropertiesView
extends javax.swing.JPanel

Displays the properties of a selected waypoint/track/route or group. This class also allows you to change the color and attributes of the selected object.

Steven
